channel.title: I need help with my webclient
channel.description:
Hello, I have made about 100 web clients in the past, and they all worked. I have quit for a few months, but now i am back. I don't think i'm doing anything wrong, i even checked a tutorial to make sure. client is Hybrid PvP v3. I honestly have tried to make my web client about 35 times now, and every time it says "Could not find main class : Client". The main class is in the folder, so i don't know what is wrong with it. If anyone knows how to fix it, please tell me.
Thank you, Mike
